post_install () {
    cat << EOF
The plugin has been installed at /usr/share/autodl-irssi. If you wish to use it
then create the local directory ~/.irssi/scripts/autorun and symbolicly link
\`autodl-irssi.pl' in /usr/share/autodl-irssi. In ~/.irssi/scripts/ *copy* the
\`AutodlIrssi' directory from /usr/share/autodl-irssi. Finally, create ~/.autodl
directory and touch \`autodl.cfg' in there.

More information can be found on the project site.
EOF
}
